## 3. Layout estructural

La app usa un layout **sidebar fija + main con topbar sticky**:

```
.app (display:flex)
├── .sidebar  — fixed left, width:260px, z-index:100, bg:white
└── .main     — margin-left:260px
    ├── .topbar   — sticky top, height:56px, z-index:50, padding:0 32px
    ├── .content  — padding:32px, padding-bottom:76px (obligatorio para .vs)
    └── .vs       — fixed bottom, z-index:200, bg:#1e2a30, left:260px
```

> `padding-bottom:76px` en `.content` es **obligatorio** — reserva espacio para el view switcher fijo.

**CSS clave del layout:**
```css
.sidebar { position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:260px; height:100vh; background:var(--blanco); border-right:1px solid var(--gris-borde); z-index:100; display:flex; flex-direction:column; overflow-y:auto; }
.main { margin-left:260px; min-height:100vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
.topbar { position:sticky; top:0; height:56px; background:var(--blanco); border-bottom:1px solid var(--gris-borde); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:0 32px; z-index:50; }
.content { padding:32px; padding-bottom:76px; flex:1; }
```

