## 6. Badges y estados

```css
/* Uso: <span class="badge badge-ok">Activo</span> */
.badge { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:20px; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.4px; }
.badge-ok   { background:#d1fae5; color:#065f46; }  /* verde */
.badge-warn { background:#fef3c7; color:#92400e; }  /* amarillo */
.badge-err  { background:#fee2e2; color:#991b1b; }  /* rojo */
.badge-info { background:var(--azul-light); color:var(--azul); }  /* azul */
.badge-gray { background:var(--gris-bg); color:var(--gris-texto); }
```

